results.name: Zero together with row 8 of the array in A163280.
link: Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients, signature (3, -3, 1).
formula: Conjecture: a(n) = A028563(n), n > 9. [_R. J. Mathar_, Jul 31 2010]
maple: A033676 := proc(n) local dvs; dvs := sort(convert(numtheory[divisors](n), list)) ; op(floor((nops(dvs)+1)/2) , dvs) ; end: A163280 := proc(n, k) local r, T ; r := 0 ; for T from k^2 by k do if A033676(T) = k then r := r+1 ; if r = n then RETURN(T) ; fi; fi; od: end: printf("0,") ; for n from 1 to 70 do printf("%d,",A163280(8,n)) ; end do ; # _R. J. Mathar_, Feb 05 2010
